ine of semi-automatic biochemistry analyzers, with variants including CliniQuant and CliniQuant Micro. The 'PRO' designation likely indicates a higher-end model within this product family. Classification corrected from 'Electronic components with optical system' to instrument type. Brand confirmed as Meril Life Sciences. Review recommended to: (1) confirm PRO model specifications differ from base CliniQuant model, (2) verify if CliniQuant PRO is marketed name or internal designation, (3) clarify relationship to CliniQuant and CliniQuant Micro variants, (4) obtain manufacturer documentation for PRO variant specifications.","proposed_recommended_action":"send_to_review","proposed_semantic_anatomy_scope":[],"proposed_semantic_brand_system":"CliniQuant","proposed_semantic_coating_default":null,"proposed_semantic_confidence":0.85,"proposed_semantic_family_group":"CliniQuant Biochemistry Analyzers","proposed_semantic_implant_class":null,"proposed_semantic_material_default":null,"proposed_semantic_parent_brand":"Meril Life Sciences","proposed_semantic_procedure_scope":["Clinical chemistry testing","Biochemical analysis","In vitro diagnostics"],"proposed_semantic_review_required":true,"proposed_semantic_system_type":"Semi-Automatic Biochemistry Analyzer","proposed_semantic_use_case_tags":["Hospital laboratory","Clinical diagnostics","Biochemistry testing","Mid-to-high throughput","Semi-automated analysis"],"proposed_web_verification_status":"externally_enriched","semantic_anatomy_scope":[],"semantic_brand_system":"CliniQuant","semantic_coating_default":null,"semantic_confidence":0.85,"semantic_conflict_codes":[],"semantic_enriched_at":"2026-03-28T10:53:48.891572+00:00","semantic_implant_class":null,"semantic_material_default":null,"semantic_parent_brand":"Meril Life Sciences","semantic_review_required":false,"semantic_rule_hits":["AUTO_LANE1_SAFE_EXTERNALLY_ENRICHED"],"semantic_system_type":"Semi-Automatic Biochemistry Analyzer"}}]
